name: Our Lady of the Red Lightsaber
description: This is an homage to George Lucas’ masterpiece Star Wars (1977). The panel is from the oil painting Our Lady of the Seven Sorrows (ca. 1518-1535) by Adriaen Isenbrandt, exhibited at the Church of Our Lady (Onze-Lieve-Vrouwekerk) in Bruges (Belgium). Look closely, she’s quite grieving, and she moves.
